HeliosX-Logger-Syslog version 0.02
==================================

HeliosX::Logger::Syslog extends the HeliosX::Logger class to provide a 
shim between HeliosX::ExtLoggerService and Sys::Syslog.  This will 
allow Helios applications using HeliosX::ExtLoggerService to log 
messages to syslogd. 


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Helios 2.00
  HeliosX::ExtLoggerService 0.02
  Sys::Syslog 0.23


